Privacy Policy for Bet on Score
Effective Date: 12/08/2025

At Bet on Score, your privacy is important to us.

We want to assure you that:

We do not collect any personal data or user information.

We do not track your behavior, device information, or usage patterns.

We do not use cookies or similar technologies.

We do not share any information with third parties, because we don't collect any to begin with.

Our app simply provides sports tips, predictions, and related content for informational purposes only.

If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, you can contact us at: betonscoretips@gmail.com
